high_descs: Move to the sink to the right of the stove
Pick up a fork from the counter
Turn to the left side of the sink
Put the fork on the plate in the cabinet
Pick up the plate with the fork on it
Move to the counter in front of the window
Put the plate on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a fork on the counter by the toaster.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the sink.
Pick up the metal fork out of the sink basin.
Turn left and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the cabinet door right in front of you and place the fork standing up on the plate.
Take the plate with the fork on it out of the cabinet and close the door.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to where the toaster is on the counter.
Place the plate with the fork on it onto the counter in front and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a fork on it onto the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Pick up the fork from the sink.
Turn to the left and look up to the cupboard.
Open the cupboard and set the fork on the tray.
Take the tray and fork out of the cupboard.
Turn around and face the toaster.
Set the tray and fork on the counter near the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Set the tray and fork on the counter near the toaster.
